-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_returns.sql
-- Deduplicate returns to one approved return per item (latest approved submission)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY return_date DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
    WHERE status = 'approved'
)
SELECT
    return_id,
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_items_with_category.sql
-- Join order_items with products and categories, handling missing categories
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.order_id,
        oi.product_id,
        oi.quantity,
        oi.unit_price,
        COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_items_with_returns.sql
-- Join items with deduped returns (LEFT JOIN preserves all items)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        ic.item_id,
        ic.order_id,
        ic.product_id,
        ic.quantity,
        ic.unit_price,
        ic.category_name,
        dr.return_id
    FROM {{ ref('int_items_with_category') }} ic
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} dr
        ON dr.item_id = ic.item_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

```sql
-- models/marts/fct_return_rates_by_category.sql
-- Calculate return rates by category
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        category_name,
        SUM(quantity) AS total_items_sold,
        SUM(CASE WHEN return_id IS NOT NULL THEN quantity ELSE 0 END) AS total_items_returned
    FROM {{ ref('int_items_with_returns') }}
    GROUP BY category_name
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    total_items_sold,
    total_items_returned,
    CASE
        WHEN total_items_sold = 0 THEN 0
        ELSE ROUND(total_items_returned::numeric / total_items_sold::numeric, 4)
    END AS return_rate
FROM source
ORDER BY category_name
